{"tid":1215055,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"買咗新iphone, 聽講可以用airdrop send 圖， 唔識用","createTime":"2019-06-13T05:58:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T06:33:42.000Z","uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"472d4d4d516a832f081ccc3c90d2ee38e617490f","tid":1215055,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:58:48.000Z","msg":"係咪咩圖都send 得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下有冇圖可以比我download<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffd379995eccd9aa28d14e63cecb0f606a2a42cf","tid":1215055,"uid":28113,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:33:42.000Z","msg":"係呀，只要save咗落「相片」裡面嘅相都可以用AirDrop send去任何iPhone<br />\n<br />\n下面簡單咗講下點做：<br />\n1）雙方都要開咗AirDrop先<br />\n喺右上角拉個control panel落嚟<br />\n喺control panel左上角<br />\n有一格可以開閂flight mode、data、藍芽、WiFi<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mk9ExTo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMk9ExTo.png&h=da2e80a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n㩒住佢會彈咗個畫面，有6樣嘢俾你㩒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tGKQEyP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtGKQEyP.png&h=926a4cdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n左下嗰個就係AirDrop開關<br />\n如果對方唔喺你contact list度<br />\n就要揀「所有人」<br />\n咁就開咁個AirDrop㗎喇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JfjX30J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJfjX30J.png&h=000b0beb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2） 用AirDrop send相/video俾人<br />\n開咗個「相片」先<br />\n揀你想send嘅相/video（可以多選）<br />\n之後㩒左下角個掣<br />\n（藍色正方框，有個向上嘅箭咀）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XcD9U4u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXcD9U4u.png&h=275a65cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n會由下至上彈咗堆選項俾你揀<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/13/143007_0a9dee25a9c8066f7dd6c4714fdecf91.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F13%2F143007_0a9dee25a9c8066f7dd6c4714fdecf91.png&h=c6710247&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果對方確定開咗AirDrop<br />\n第一行就會見到對方個icon<br />\n一㩒落去就會send request過去<br />\n對方可以揀收定唔收<br />\n假設佢揀咗收，自然就會send過去<br />\n<br />\n完成！"}]}